{"tid":804163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勞資糾紛】澳洲網紅少女 墨西哥富豪遊艇上離奇死","createTime":"2018-09-02T23:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T00:19:27.000Z","uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc4501354099bcea9fbbf0d414215ab2714e1f9","tid":804163,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:02:50.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名網紅少女在一名墨西哥富豪的遊艇上離奇死亡。<br />\n<br />\n涉事遊艇Mayan Queen IV六層高，屬於墨西哥礦業大亨巴Alberto Baill&egrave;res，上周停靠希臘Kefalonia島。20歲女死者Sinead McNamara在遊艇上工作已經四個月。<br />\n<br />\n少女上周五清晨被發現倒臥在船尾，身體被繩纏住。船上醫生及港口人員為她急救，及後用直升機將她送往雅典一間醫院，但在途中證實不治。"},{"pid":"99819f44bbdf8f73d802c5d7632e21e35310507a","tid":804163,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:05:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9f1124f425f8e27625236913b9f7ec7b6297ff2","tid":804163,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:07:55.000Z","msg":"玩咩玩到咁激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04af3249b4063c2ca80fd002f2b3dc6bb373fb21","tid":804163,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩咩玩到咁激&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n玩繩！"},{"pid":"d046441a17c6f156d7506cbefa54c43d47666275","tid":804163,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:18:49.000Z","msg":"網紅=雞"},{"pid":"9e050858c3699c2ee94ba61182a58a702f69b75e","tid":804163,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc77c9e3013f5c107c1aa381b61f31a46b1b416","tid":804163,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e050858c3699c2ee94ba61182a58a702f69b75e","tid":804163,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"工作<img src=\